                                                                    <p>We are now finally ready to upgrade our project to Symfony 3. How do we do that?
It's a simple, 2 step process.</p>
<p>First, in <code>composer.json</code> change the <code>symfony/symfony</code> key, to <code>3.0.*</code>:</p>
